      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Move the cabinet(s) to the installation location with a
forklift or a low profile 21 inch pallet jack by lifting from the
sides.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <hazardstatement type="warning">
                  <messagepanel>
                     <typeofhazard>Tipping hazard</typeofhazard>
                     <howtoavoid>The cabinet is top-heavy. Move the cabinet carefully with
a forklift or a low profile 21 inch pallet jack by lifting from the
sides.</howtoavoid>
                  </messagepanel>
               </hazardstatement>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Remove the right side panel with ground strap from the
UPS cabinet and install the side panel on the right side of the top
entry cabinet.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Remove_Kick_Plates_TSK_0000161962.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Install_Seismic_Anchoring_Option_0000161960.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Only in systems with adjacent battery cabinet(s):<xref href="Prepare_for_Cables_on_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_with_an_Adjacent_Battery_Cabinet_0000114606.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Prepare_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_for_Bottom_Cable_Entry_TSK_0000125402.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Prepare_for_Cables_on_the_Top_Entry_Cabinet_0000125352.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Install_the_Top_Entry_Cabinet_Option_TSK_0000161461.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Connect_the_Power_Cables_Connect_the_Power_Cables_on_the_25-50_kVA_UPS_0000161460.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="task"/>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>
               <xref href="Route_the_Control_Cables_through_the_Top_Entry_Cabinet_to_the_25-50_kVA__0000125372.xml"
                     format="dita"
